<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="3779764" n="331r"/>
<opener>Viro Reverendo atque Celeberrimo 
                        <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119112450">Jacobo Hermanno</rs>
                        <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117205508">Jac: Christophorus Iselius</rs> S. P. D.</opener>
<p>Ego vero avide nunc opperiar adventum tuum, quando post octa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>vum mensem exspectari Te jubes, neque, nisi Te prius amplexus fuero
                        <lb/>ac de Te nobis prima quaque opportunitate vindicando consilia con<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>[t]ulero, iter quod in idem istud ver, si DEUS faveat, constitui, sum
                        <lb/>[a]ggressurus. Venias modo salvus et incolumis, et cathedram tuam ei
                        <lb/>[r]elinquas, qui <rs type="person" key="GND">Caesenati</rs> illi sit quam dissimilimus. Facis profecto,
                        <lb/>[u]t non optime de acumine ac peritia Mathematicorum Ita<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lorum sentiamus, quando tam multos admirari hunc <rs type="person" key="GND">homi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>[n]em</rs> scribis, atque ejus subtilitatem Geometricam praedicare. Uti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nam brevi ipsum Cel. nostri <rs type="person" key="GND">Bernoullij</rs> dictata deficiant, cre<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>de mihi,
                        <lb/>----- 	moveat cornicula risum
                        <lb/>Furtivis nudata coloribus;
                        <lb/>planeque inopem ac nudum videbunt stare, cujus divitias commen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dabant. Quod me in Viri Illustris <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-116980257">Apostoli Zeni</rs> benevolentiam
                        <lb/>insinuaveris, vehementer Te amo. Si is scripta mea non invi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>[s]us legat, audebo fortassis etiam ceterorum, quae in Philolo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>[g]ico genere hactenus edidi, ad ipsum curare exempla. Tu modo
                        <lb/>[p]erge obsecro Eum mihi conciliare, et me illius observan<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>[t]issimum esse, et semper fore fac resciscat. Quid agat, ac
                        <lb/>[]um etiamdum <rs type="person" key="GND">Barcinone</rs> horeat Clar: <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119291967">Fardella</rs>, pariter
                        <lb/>[c]upio ex Te cognoscere. Si ad eum Tute scribas, valde velim mei me<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>moriam a Te ipsi refricari.</p> <closer>Vale meum decus, et ama me
                        <lb/>porro qui Te pereo. <dateline>Datum <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basileae</rs> <date when="1712-08-04">prid. Non. Sextil. 1712</date>.</dateline></closer>
</div>
</body>
</text></TEI>